# Triangulation method for computer vision

Let $m_1$ and $m_2$ be two corresponding points and $P_1$ and $P_2$ be camera matrices.

The problem is finding $X$ satisfying $m_1=P_1X$ and $m_2=P_2X$

$$m_1\times P_1X=0$$

