Let $\tau$ be triangulation method used to compute 3D space point $M$ 

$$
M = \tau(m_1, m_2, P_1, P_2)
$$

Let $F$ be fundamental matrix. The two rays correspoinding to points $m_1$ and $m_2$ will meet in space iff the points satisfy:

